	<h3>Why would I learn this language?</h3>
	
	<p>BASIC is a simple language which is easy to learn. It provides a basic set of semantic constructs and data types. There are many <tt>free software</tt> implementations, but unfortunately the most typically used implementation is proprietary (Microsoft Visual Basic).</p>
	
